item.title: CVE-2018-1002209|2024-09-16T19:25:10.760Z -- quazip -- quazip
item.description: QuaZIP before 0.7.6 is vulnerable to directory traversal, allowing attackers to write to arbitrary files via a ../ (dot dot slash) in a Zip archive entry that is mishandled during extraction. This vulnerability is also known as 'Zip-Slip'.
